import sys

def cocktail(A,B,C,I,J,K):
    if A/I < B/J and A/I <= C/K:
        return A/I, B-A*J/I, C-A*K/I
    elif B/J < A/I and B/J <= C/K:
        return A-B*I/J, B/J, C-B*K/J
    else:
        return A-C*I/K, B-C*J/K, C/K

    I,J,K = map(float, sys.stdin.readline().split())
    print('%0.6f %0.6f %0.6f' % cocktail(A,B,C,I,J,K))

    return (A - max_cocktails*I, B - max_cocktails*J, C - max_cocktails*K)

def main():
    A, B, C, I, J, K = get_input()
    (A, B, C) = get_leftovers(A, B, C, I, J, K)
    print("%.6f %.6f %.6f" % (A, B, C))

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
